3-Digit Counter Circuit

Description
A digital counter system using 555 Timer as a clock source, 74160 and 4511 ICs for counting and decoding, and 7-segment displays for visualization.

Components
- 555 Timer IC  
- 74160 Counter IC  
- 4511 BCD to 7-Segment Decoder IC  
- 7-Segment Displays (x3)

Features
- 555 provides clock pulses for 74160  
- 4511 converts counter output to BCD  
- Real-time numeric display on 7-segments  
- Designed and tested in Proteus
